\begin{frame}{Issues}
There are a number of issues associated with ESG
\begin{itemize}[<+-| alert@+>]
\pause
\item The rise of passive investment may conflict with ESG aims
\begin{itemize}
\item but it gives \emph{owners} a broader perspective
\end{itemize}
\item The difficulty of measurement and lack of standardisation 
\begin{itemize}
\item lack of benchmarks 
